videos.description: Maryland fakes the field goal and holder Ryan Brand takes the snap and is stopped at the 1-yard line.
videos.headline: Maryland stopped on fake field goal attempt

videos.description: Maryland QB Max Bortenschlager connects with DJ Turner for the 22-yard catch putting Maryland at the eight-yard line.
videos.headline: Turner's diving grab puts Maryland inside 10

videos.description: Maryland QB Max Bortenschlager takes it himself for a seven-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Bortenschlager rush TD gives Maryland first score

videos.description: Minnesota RB Rodney Smith takes the handoff up the middle for a one-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Smith's 1-yard plunge knots score

videos.description: Minnesota QB  Conor Rhoda is intercepted by Josh Woods at the Maryland five-yard line.
videos.headline: Minnesota red zone trip ends with INT

videos.description: Maryland QB Max Bortenschlager connects with DJ Moore for a 27-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Moore snags deep ball to give Maryland lead

videos.description: Conor Rhoda hooks up with  Brandon Lingen for a seven-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Lingen extends to tie score for Minnesota

videos.description: Conor Rhoda floats a jump ball to Tyler Johnson for the great 25-yard catch.
videos.headline: Johnson's great grab puts Minnesota in red zone

videos.description: Minnesota QB Conor Rhoda connects with Tyler Johnson for a 27-yard pass and puts them at the Maryland 20-yard line.
videos.headline: Johnson's big play puts Minnesota into red zone

videos.description: Minnesota QB Conor Rhoda lays it out for Eric Carter who makes a crazy diving grab to move them to the Maryland one-yard line.
videos.headline: Carter's diving grab brings Minnesota to one-yard line

videos.description: Minnesota RB Shannon Brooks powers forward for the one-yard touchdown late in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Brooks 1-yard TD run pulls Minnesota even

videos.description: Minnesota RB Ty Johnson takes the handoff 34 yards to the house for the game's decisive score.
videos.headline: Johnson breaks free for game-winning TD
